<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="swallow-v">swallow <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'swɒləʊ/    美 /'swɑːloʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>吞下；咽下：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He put a grape into his mouth and <strong>swallowed</strong> it <strong>whole</strong>. 
他把一粒葡萄放进嘴里，整个吞了下去。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>抑制：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She swallowed her anger and turned to face him. 
她忍住怒气，转过身来面对着他。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="swallow-up">swallow up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>吞没；淹没；用尽：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The ship was swallowed up by the wave. 
船被大浪吞没了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The extra money was soon swallowed up. 
这笔额外的钱很快就花光了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The smog swallowed up the whole city. 
雾霾笼罩着整个城市。</p></div></div>